tsps
Class TSPS

java.lang.Object
  tsps.TSPS

public class TSPS
extends java.lang.Object

OSC Message is structured like this: address: TSPS/person/ + ordered id (i.e. TSPS/person/0) argument 1: pid; argument 2: age; argument 3: centroid.x; argument 4: centroid.y; argument 5: velocity.x; argument 6: velocity.y; argument 7: boundingRect.x; argument 8: boundingRect.y; argument 9: boundingRect.width; argument 10: boundingRect.height;
